              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13126933-lata?shelf=bipoc-actor">bipoc-actor</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2055850008" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7684012805332941403">Lovely little book I picked up on impulse. Beautiful collages of Peter having fun in the snow. Simple, sweet story of a young child on a winter&apos;s day.</span>
  <span id="freeText7684012805332941403" style="display:none">Lovely little book I picked up on impulse. Beautiful collages of Peter having fun in the snow. Simple, sweet story of a young child on a winter's day.</span>
